        SELECT 1
        FROM [Users] AS [u]
        WHERE (([u].[Email] = @__item_Email_0) AND ([u].[Email] IS NOT NULL AND @__item_Email_0 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([u].[Email] IS NULL AND @__item_Email_0 IS NULL)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
